Social or racial groups has in influencing consumers food choices 

199
00:14:21,290 --> 00:14:26,790
This research found college students were more likely to choose healthy food

200
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:29,860
in the presence of an observer of a different race 

201
00:14:29,860 --> 00:14:32,950
As opposed to an observer from their own race 

202
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:37,340
