210
00:15:07,110 --> 00:15:10,190
However , this number was thirty one percent

211
00:15:10,190 --> 00:15:14,070
When in the presence of an unknown student from another university 

212
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:18,760
Other experiments showed similar results based on racial group

213
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:21,320
