269
00:20:32,270 --> 00:20:34,750
No matter how calculated they may be 

270
00:20:35,360 --> 00:20:38,340
But this should not stop you from taking risks 

271
00:20:38,340 --> 00:20:42,400
As risks are necessary if you want your business to succeed 

272
00:20:43,260 --> 00:20:45,500
Some risks may not work out 

273
00:20:45,700 --> 00:20:47,940
But an optimistic risk taker

274
00:20:47,940 --> 00:20:51,660
Will always look at failure as an opportunity to learn 

275
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:57,460
The willingness to experiment with new ideas is key to business growth 

276
00:20:58,160 --> 00:21:00,040
As the old saying goes 

277
00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:02,680
Nothing ventured , nothing gained 

278
00:21:03,770 --> 00:21:08,090
Failure will teach you how to think and plan strategically 

279
00:21:08,560 --> 00:21:12,640
But just remember that not all risks are good ones 

280
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:14,040
And when you fail 

281
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:16,400
Learn from it and move forward 

282
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:19,900
Since most people tend to avoid risk 

283
00:21:19,900 --> 00:21:22,800
Businesses that are brave enough to take risks

284
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:25,360
Already have a competitive advantage 

285
00:21:25,990 --> 00:21:29,310
They are the ones setting the standard with new ideas 

286
00:21:29,310 --> 00:21:32,070
Fresh offers , and bold inventions 

287
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:36,320
Risk takers are best at adapting in difficult times 

288
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:41,800
Simply put , when most individuals stay away from risk 

289
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:44,680
It means less competition for risk takers 

290
00:21:45,560 --> 00:21:49,330
We don't know if you'll achieve what these risk takers have achieved 

291
00:21:49,330 --> 00:21:51,860
But for as long as you want to stay safe 

